"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**Scope** — Product Design, Research & Web Design · **Timeline** — 5 Days\\n\\n[https://www.figma.com/file/yzIzRa4k2EPEss5usjCUT6/Port-Finance?node-id=84%3A2370](https://www.figma.com/file/yzIzRa4k2EPEss5usjCUT6/Port-Finance?node-id=84%3A2370)\\n\\nThe whole lending, borrowing, depositing thing was a little overwhelming at first, but as I started exploring more tools like Compoun.Finance, and some De-Fi videos, I got the hang of it.\\n\\n### Design Style & Direction\\n\\n![Port.Finance Visual Language](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Rau4mGmepiTvsYvXTlI-o.png?height=2568&width=4440&&&size=large)\\n\\n### Markets\\n\\n![Markets — Old & New](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8irTE1ZE4h5f4WTHkEMlQ.png?height=1784&width=6372&&&size=large)\\n\\n### Home\\n\\n![Dashboard Tab — Old & New](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/7oOkDmXLrAwbWurLXwT5M.png?height=1784&width=6372&&&size=large)\\n\\nDeposit\\n\\nBorrow\\n\\nLend\\n\\nMint\\n\\n### Empty States\\n\\n![Empty States for Depositing into a coin, Deposit Card, Annual Projected Yield, Collaterals, Loans, Risk Factors and Positions.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/kqsq1F4Op8k5qgLQ_xG47.png?height=3480&width=4320&&&size=large)\\n\\nLanding Page\",\"timestamp\":1640832413,\"title\":\"Port.Finance Redesign + Critique \"},\"digest\":\"6n2pNWk3Ywsnel7yTiiGabQmfKA85MqI8G5Wf0urxYg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x587A1c24Ed0124EfA68155218a1eb68b7A687f24\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"usHLKYsRLpSA_BYHseHBhYglrERHBrX3m9CEMG5u4So\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9DbS-jm7FAAzh6Ljb8DY2DL6jwbR84XKXW1NVHZKA6Y\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"u9eYoIokqJ34Wl4aHDf1YGOqzJLmUf5pyscci-DnmYbO1GeP4m3ok9tWrPsOlJji8AlPKvIIb2crxIGDTk9Iig\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd32f48c3b6e210bf55895ed50027fc8f8dbee156280e293ddc0b9c121a1ca6786063e05875c2db5c8cf5a9d3baa92ce7bf225dddda